  "title": "Delicate Sour Brazilian Thai Eggplant Skillet",
  "description": "A sour and fluffy solo dinner dish featuring Thai eggplant, miso marinate, and diabetic friendly ingredients, blending Brazilian and Thai flavors.",
  "cuisine": "Brazilian Thai",
