  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large skillet over medium high heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced Thai eggplant and cook for 3 minutes on each side.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the miso paste and lime juice.",
    "Pour the miso lime mixture over the eggplant and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with fresh cilantro or scallions if desired."
  ],
